Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:46.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:54.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用这对朱色翅膀掩去一切丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.43,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,000)}思念如附着的污渍般挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这地球上生存着的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:18.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人窒息般地紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:25.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝视着镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:30.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了隐藏自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:38.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去刺伤那些温柔善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:44.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:50.53,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朱色的翅膀轻盈地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:56.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烈火般的热吻一次次重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:09.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就用这最后一吻收敛起热情奔放的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:06.13,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳把热情的目光投向这边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:11.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}真想好好享受这夏天 这阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:18.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天会发生什么令人激情澎湃的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:23.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的不安点缀着这美妙的期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:31.03,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}夏天的回忆涌现在我脑际
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:36.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}晶亮的碎片注入天空大海充满世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:41.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,100)}低声私语请求你的拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.73,0:24:44.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}顽皮地挑逗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:49.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}不需要你做出暧昧的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:57.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,000)}那一瞬 我已经预感到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.63,0:25:01.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,300)}在这热情洋溢的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是我住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那里就是一直在看的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下面就是到健的家我们走过的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对面是很多人居住的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世界很大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快乐 可爱的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看姐姐身材是很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说是皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能脱的都能脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 花了很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但怎么样 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是和孙女在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个... 一定是很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,明有这个的话 光也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 那个衣服是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我从明天开始上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但竟然能这么快办好入学手续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个没有必要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事情都能办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说没有不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是大家在的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为是快乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里一定有新的邂逅在等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,第五话 学校的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为并不是那么值得期待的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,光每天都在说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好像连走路也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 我喜欢走路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走路的时候 能遇见很多的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看见很多颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,学校是什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,比街上的颜色少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你 是你啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这头发的颜色是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,染这种颜色是犯校规的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,光的头发颜色是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是只有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在介绍转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫星之光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从什么地方来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,星之很奇怪的姓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,第一印象很深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么不明白的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就问班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫吉田真由 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们原来不是神 也不是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很平常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,平常的伦理认为的人之善恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们遵循着这个守则
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们有了人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和你说话的 不是神 也不是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这些只是没有感情的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和人相比有着不同的心...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,辽少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,和想象的不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但她的脸就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,失望的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很失望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,健 说失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不能原谅 不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是有点跟不上当初的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想学校应该是每天都充满生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,洋溢着青春的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,确实不只是这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这该不会是大家的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有苦 有甜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有点原始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不希望都是甜的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 就像把同一个游戏重玩很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,学校每天都不能不来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像同样的游戏玩了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,比较相似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,学校要是像游戏一样能重新开始的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以首先要找女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,学校果然是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在学校还能每天和大家一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真像你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 早和你说学校是什么地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想还是不要太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么大家每天要来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家是都喜欢学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还是讨厌学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次打 真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始进行避难训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请按老师指示 快速避难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请问这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没听过广播吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 只不过是训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 这个学校也真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,星之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真想偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,应该一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,健 这么快就被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,经常做这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,说不是经常 其实今天是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认为这不好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但学校就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但...但是像刚才比赛那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那样 很惨 很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为什么让我做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但...但是我很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要比常人更努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上大家就很累了 尽是做些出丑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,学校就是大家都要做一样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟屁虫也有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我...讨厌学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就该把它破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾 地震这种灾难时有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以大家要随时做好被袭的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,健
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,光 光 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我醒了就在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把我说成那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没有伤员 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 吉田你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把学校破坏的是你 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,详细说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太麻烦了先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好好解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,突然态度转变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请各位听好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在我身体的周围有蓝色的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的信息都在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收周围的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而形成了这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是睡了很久 那个结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,先不说这个 为什么把学校给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是本来没有这个打算的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,醒来的时候发现被困在柱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以把柱子给破坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一直睡着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样 因为听到了主人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是叫光大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,样子也没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始我没有明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你是光的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就像贴身保镖不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她也有怪东西跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它不是怪东西 它是克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要温柔一点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实不像我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说它也有主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才什么也没有感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也许是兄弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一副很熟悉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在主人身边有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是光让你觉醒的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没有叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只是根据光的气息自己觉醒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说我只是觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,事情是怎么样我可不负责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它也要住在我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,HELLO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,新面孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我爱纽·有司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天还要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但谁都不会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事可以做的话 我想做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道有什么可以做 先去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好像只有工作人员在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爱纽·有司请帮助他们工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁的最新产品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,星之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,记不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个一定是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,受刺激记忆混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但星之你没事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 醒之前一直等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么吉田会在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,纪念册
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我去年刚成为班长 那个时候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是要找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看着这个不仅能想起学校的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,做这之前的事 和之后发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦的事 快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对吉田来说是很重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多 像吉田一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像明白一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田 不 大家都很喜欢学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也许所有的感觉并不都是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌的事也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但有美好的回忆 总的来说就是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了什么奇怪的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就像光所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来的人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我有想拿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,结果大家都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带便当来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要帮很多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋啊 都说工地禁止入内了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么死板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们来说是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就一些时间也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣 所以来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 那么不高兴的脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是女儿嫁人时 父母的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只要光找到快乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,健 请看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天这里没有这么多的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多漂亮的颜色 红的 黄的 金的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都是些没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,马上所有的东西都会变回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,乏味的每天 那样真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为发生了意外情况决定暑假提前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,光 你听到了吗 是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么学校...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就不上了 因为放假了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那太过分了 才刚刚体会到了学校的好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 到了秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,马上第二学期就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗 真期待秋天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要现在说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 在这之前是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,学校之外也有很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你的 光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.63,0:25:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫竹本健
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.33,0:25:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假就是要山上野营 不管怎么都明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.93,0:25:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.13,0:25:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想让光她们看看常人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.53,0:25:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么爱纽·有司也来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.33,0:25:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,詹妮夫也来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.13,0:25:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下回 这个丑与美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.83,0:25:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,水边的伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也是希望什么也别发生
